WAF can be integrated with  Amazon CloudFront, the Application Load Balancer (ALB), Amazon API Gateway, and AWS AppSync.

- create a webACL(web access control list) , give it and cloudwatch metric a name.
- choose the resource type, ex: cloudfront distributuon which is global service or ALB, apigateway which are regional.
- add the resource which cloudfront distribution id.
- next in add rules and rulegroups, choose the existing rules from the dropdown or create your custom new rules(ACL).
- ip sets: Ip sets are created to restrict the users who are allowed to access from that ip range.
